pageContext.claim: “We did a lot of wall in San Diego, where we needed it very badly, where they wanted it very badly.”
pageContext.analysis: What Trump is talking about is fencing. San Diego does not support construction of the wall and it is not being constructed there. The Republican mayor of San Diego has said, "We already have a safe and secure border in San Diego built by the federal government." The city council passed a resolution opposing the border wall.
